<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Thank you for your message!</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333; } h1
      { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      p { margin-bottom: 20px; } .message { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding:
      20px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .message-title {
      font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; } .message-body { margin-bottom:
      20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank you for your message!</h1>
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We appreciate your interest in our
      products and services.</p>
    <p>We have received your message and will respond as soon as possible. In
      the meantime, feel free to browse our website or contact us if you have
      any further questions.</p>
    <div class="message">
      <div class="message-title">Your Message:</div>
      <div class="message-body">
        <p>{{message}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>FIN Investments Inc.</p>
  </body>
</html>